title: Dita Von Teese

description:
The Queen of Burlesque Dita Von Teese is on GOOD FOR YOU talking to Whitney about fetishes, sitting on cakes, Mae West, advice from Madonna, and Whitney getting peed on in the shower.  Whitney also tries on some lingerie from Dita's collection and finally figures out her actual bra size.  Dita's New Year's Eve Gala Show has been postponed but please check out: https://linktr.ee/Ditavonteese for updates and tickets.
